Some help to use git

### STEP 1 ###
git clone https://github.com/fabriziotappero/freerangefactory.org.git
cd freerangefactory.org

### STEP 2 ###
do your modifications
git status or git status -a or use gitk
git add .
git commit -m 'added some good stuff'

### STEP 3 ###
git push origin gh-pages
your website is now available on:
http://fabriziotappero.github.io/freerangefactory.org/

more here here:
http://rogerdudler.github.io/git-guide
